| **No input validation** | Added query parameter validation with type checking |
| **No error handling** | Added try-catch blocks and global error handler |
| **No 404 handling** | Added 404 middleware |
| **No graceful shutdown** | Added SIGTERM handler |
| **Information disclosure** | Error details hidden in production |
| **No logging** | Added error logging |

