| Security headers | HIGH | Security | Use helmet.js |
| Rate limiting | MEDIUM | Security | Add express-rate-limit |
| CORS | MEDIUM | Security | Configure properly |
| Authentication/Authorization | HIGH | Security | Add auth checks |
| Logging | MEDIUM | Operations | Add morgan |
| Environment config | LOW | Configuration | Use dotenv |

